# Frontend Environment Variables

# Auto-detection is ENABLED by default:
# The application automatically detects the current hostname and points to the correct API:
# - If on localhost:3001 -> API calls go to http://localhost:3003
# - If on helpdesk.hubblehox.ai -> API calls go to https://helpdesk.hubblehox.ai

# Optional: Override auto-detection by uncommenting these (usually not needed)
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3003
# VITE_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3003

# Production examples (for reference, auto-detection will use these)
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://helpdesk.hubblehox.ai
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://helpdesk.hubblehox.ai
